name: Z-ONE/Monster E
text:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. The ATK of all other "Timelord" monsters you control become 4000. The ATK of this card is equal to the combined ATK of all "Timelord" monsters you control.

-I Summon "Sephylon, the Ultimate Timelord"!-

Hidden Effect
If this card would be destroyed, you can destroy 1 other "Timelord" monster you control instead.
